  <brief_title>Bleeding in Patients Undergoing CABG During Dual Antiplatelet Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Bleeding in Patients Undergoing Urgent CABG During Dual Antiplatelet Therapy Including the New P2Y12 Receptor Inhibitors Prasugrel and Ticagrelor</official_title>
  <sponsors>
