  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to evaluate surgery-related bleeding and mortality in patients
      needing acute coronary artery bypass grafting with or without valve replacement during dual
      antiplatelet therapy with aspirin and a P2Y12 receptor blocker (Clopidogrel, Prasugrel,
      Ticagrelor)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
